        <mxCell id="hQFJinEqyon_zx6QdwSI-4" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;" value="&amp;nbsp;- set WorkRequest status to SCHEDULING&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;- load results from Cache for Model&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;- if all results returned from cache:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; - upload result to S3&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; - set work request status to COMPLETED&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;- else, request a new ModelInstance&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;- if success, set status to PROCESSING&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;- else, set status back to QUEUED&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
